                        p
                            strong Eligibility
                        p By registering to use a Bitradex Account, you have affirmed that you are at least 18 years old and are an individual, legal person or other organization with full legal capacity to enter into this User Agreement between you and Bitradex. If you are not, you and your guardian shall undertake all consequences resulting from your actions and Bitradex shall have the right to cancel or freeze your account in addition to filing claims against you and your guardian for compensation.
