                        p By accessing and using Bitradex and any of its services, you acknowledge and declare that you are not on any trade or economic sanctions lists, such as the United Nations Security Council Sanctions List and its equivalent. Bitradex maintains the right to select its markets and jurisdictions to operate and may restrict or deny its services to certain countries. The content of this Agreement shall not be excluded from the laws of the country under which the user belongs. Bitradex maintains its stance that prohibited users are not to use or access Bitradex and any of its services.
                        p    
                            strong Description of services
                        p Bitradex provides an online digital asset trading platform (crypto to crypto) for products commonly known as cryptographic tokens, digital tokens or cryptographic currency. Bitradex does not provide fiat trading capabilities on its platform and as such is not subjected to the stringent regulations that come with it. Bitradex functions as a trading platform provider and is not a buyer or seller in trades made between traders. Bitradex is also not a market maker. Traders must register and open an account with Bitradex and deposit digital assets prior to commencement of trading. Traders may request the withdrawal of their digital assets, subject to the limitations as stated in the Terms and Conditions.
                        p Bitradex strives to maintain the accuracy of information posted on its website however it cannot guarantee the accuracy, suitability, reliability, completeness, performance or fitness for purpose of the content through the website, and will not accept liability for any loss or damage that may arise directly or indirectly from the content. Information on Bitradex website can be subjected to change without notice and is provided for the primary purpose of facilitating users to arrive at independent decisions. Bitradex does not provide investment or advisory advice and will have no liability for the use or interpretation of information as stated in its website or other communication mediums. All users of Bitradex must understand that there are risks involved in trading. Bitradex encourages all users to exercise prudence and trade responsibly within their own means.
                        p While Bitradex emphasises platform security to ensure the continuity and security of its services (announcements will be made in event of downtime/maintenance), it will be non-accountable to Act of God, malicious targeted hacking, terrorist attacks and other unforeseen circumstances. Bitradex reserves the right to cancel, rollback or block transactions of all type on its platform in event of abnormal transactions. Bitradex will not ask for any password from its users nor ask users to transfer funds that are not listed on its trading platform. Users are encouraged to exercise prudence in dealing with discounts or promotions that could lead to them getting scammed. While the list is non-exhaustive, you agree that Bitradex will not be held responsible for any losses arising from the situations stated above.
                        p By using Bitradex and any of its services, you declare that all information to Bitradex in connection with these Terms are true, accurate and complete.
                        p 
