                        p Bitradex prioritizes maintaining the safety of those user funds entrusted to us and has implemented industry standard protections for our platform. With that said, there are account-level risks that are created by individual user actions. We request that you understand the need to independently take safety precautions to protect your own account and personal information.
                        p You shall be solely responsible for the safekeeping of your Bitradex account and password on your own, and you shall be responsible for all activities under your log-in email, Bitradex account and password (including but not limited to information disclosure, information posting, consent to or submission of various rules and agreements by clicking on the website, online renewal of agreement, etc.).
